the assessment facilitators are comprised of a faculty member and the associate dean from each college, as well as the director of assessment. in addition, the library and division of student affairs both have a representative. the purposes of this group include reviewing and analyzing program assessment reports, sharing best practices on program assessment, and aiding departments and programs in implementing sound assessment practices.tianqin (kelly) shiinterim accreditation directormeg virickassociate deanradha aravamudhanadjunct professor, aerospace engineeringlynne andonianprofessor, occupational therapyvalerie mendozaassociate professor, art and art historycolton saylor, lecturer, english and comparative literaturecontact theteam membersdirectly or email us by area:accreditation@sjsu.eduacademicassessment@sjsu.eduonline@sjsu.eduprogramplanning@sjsu.eduhours: mondays to fridays from 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. closed for most holidays and for lunch daily, 12:00 p.m. to 1:00 pm.